@startuml
[*] --> ACTIVE_CLOSED

ACTIVE_CLOSED --> ACTIVE_OPEN : open
ACTIVE_CLOSED --> DEPLETED : consume/correct to zero
ACTIVE_CLOSED --> DISCARDED : discard

ACTIVE_OPEN --> DEPLETED : consume/correct to zero
ACTIVE_OPEN --> DISCARDED : discard

DEPLETED --> ARCHIVED : archive
DISCARDED --> ARCHIVED : archive

ARCHIVED --> [*]
@enduml
